data.title: School of Medicine
data.meta_description: I grew up on the coast of Maine and went to the University of Vermont to study Neuroscience. After a quick stint in Wyoming following college, I returned east to study medicine in New Hampshire. I feel lucky to have had my education take me to such wonderful places throughout New England and I am thrilled to spend the next chapter in Utah.
